init_text:
A woman has been dating guy after guy, but it never seems to work out. She’s unaware that she’s actually been dating the same guy over and over; a shapeshifter who’s fallen for her, and is certain he’s going to get it right this time.

One day,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Since she has a lot of time on her hands, she decides to meet him for coffee.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: When she arrives to the coffee shop, her date already has a cup in front of him.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "This is for you." he says, pointing at the cup.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Oh, I don't need one." he replies.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Oh, so do you come here often?" she asks.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I come here every week." he replies.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I thought you said you just had a drink here last week." she says.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I wanted to see if you'd let me have one more shot with you."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I don't even know who you are."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She was so shocked, she couldn't move.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He looked at her and said, "I'm sorry.
